Quote: WAFER CHARLOTTE ... Madeira cake, cut out centre. One white of egg (beaten) ... with icing sugar; put round outside ... put on pink wafer biscuits, tie round with tape; fill centre with fruit ... jelly ... beat cream and flavour, pile on top; take off tape and tie with a ribbon to match your flowers.
